[Pp][Rr][Nn]
[Pp][Rr][Nn].*
[Cc][Oo][Mm][0-9]
[Cc][Oo][Mm][0-9].*
[Ll][Pp][Tt][0-9]
[Ll][Pp][Tt][0-9].*

